model.name: Mazet2020 - model of the PI cycle

body.p:
PI cycle Core Model 


Global Quantities = free + bound PL for PI, PIP2, PI4P, PIP3, PI34P2, DAG, PA.
For PI initial quantity added in GQ is in organelle membranes
NB: all labeled [xxgl] in plots

select L.GPCR for GPCR simulations in Events
select R for GqPCR receptor number simulations
relevant plots = Core - IP3-DAG - PI3K-GPCR


NB: 
Built using Particle Numbers
flux are not properly calculated (enzymes are not written as modifiers)
